Development
===========

* source code is available using [Git][1]:

    $ git clone git://anonscm.debian.org/qa/debsources.git

* the Git repository is also available [via Gitweb][2]

* please report bugs via mail at `info@sources.debian.net`, after checking that
  your issue isn't already listed in the [BUGS file][3]

* for Debsources discussions please use the [debian-qa mailing list][4] and the
  `#debian-qa` IRC channel on [OFTC][5]

[1]: http://git-scm.com/
[2]: http://anonscm.debian.org/gitweb/?p=qa/debsources.git
[3]: http://anonscm.debian.org/gitweb/?p=qa/debsources.git;a=blob;f=BUGS;hb=refs/heads/bugs
[4]: http://lists.debian.org/debian-qa/
[5]: http://www.oftc.net/


Dependencies
============

Webapp
------

Debian packages:

- apache2
- libapache2-mod-fcgid (for FastCGI deployment)
- libapache2-mod-wsgi (for WSGI deployment)
- libjs-highlight
- python-debian
- python-flask
- python-flaskext.wtf
- python-flup (for FastCGI deployment)
- python-magic
- tango-icon-theme

Pip packages:

- flask-sqlalchemy


Infrastructure
--------------

(work in progress, likely incomplete)

Debian packages:

- apache2-utils
- debmirror
- rrdtool
